data.description: Welcome home to 2037 Dewey Dr! From the minute you pull into the driveway, you are surrounded by the feeling of “welcome home”.  This one owner home is located in the sought after Aquia Harbour neighborhood with the Aquia Creek in your backyard! Enjoy swinging on your covered front porch in the quiet cul-de-sac. This home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, main level laundry room,  living room with a gas fireplace and tons of natural light overlooking the Creek.  The oversized 2 car garage includes several storage cabinets and shelves along with several workbenches!  Step right out onto your large rear deck to grill, hang out and enjoy the view of Aquia Creek. The backyard is flat, fully fenced and includes a storage shed. Aquia Harbour is a gated community conveniently featuring 2 Pools, Police Department,  Fire Department, Marina w/Boat Ramp & Fishing Pier, Kayak/Canoe Launches, Golf Course w/Pro Shop, Putting Green, Driving Range & Clubhouse and Restaurant, Horse Stables, Riding Areas/Trails & Pens,  PreSchool,  8 Parks w/Tot Lots, Tennis, Basketball courts.  A short car ride away and you have access to I95, HOV lanes, Quantico Marine Base, commuter lots, shopping and dining. Come take a look and fall in love with 2037 Dewey Dr! Home is being sold as is.
